latestPosts.caption:
Where would you like to go next?

Here are some pictures from my Budapest trip in November—never too late to share!

Buda and Pest were both incredible, each with its own charm. The thermal baths were the perfect way to unwind, and the Parliament building? Absolutely breathtaking—the most stunning one I’ve ever seen. I also had some unforgettable meals, from comforting chicken paprikash to an exquisite fine dining experience at Salt, one of the city’s best restaurants. Budapest lived up to the expectations!

#budapest #travel #christmasmarkets #stylouette #fashion

Finally sharing my unfiltered Germany travel moments (Nov ‘24)✨ Wandered through the charming towns on the Romantic Road, indulged in amazing hot chocolate, food and beer, got a car tech update from the BMW museum and soaked in every bit of the Christmas magic.
